NAME
     ShadeDist - set shading of distances

SYNOPSIS
     ShadeDist ( none | flat | gouraud | phong |
	 dots | lines )

DESCRIPTION
     Set the shading method for distances if they are
     displayed as cylinders.

	 none:    no shading
	 flat:    polygons shaded in uniform color
	 gouraud: color interpolated between vertices
	 phong:   normals interpolated, highest quality
	 dots:    draw surface using dots
	 lines:   draw surface using lines

     Not all graphics devices support all shading methods.

EXAMPLE
     ShadeDist phong

SEE ALSO
     SelectDist, StyleDist, ColorDist

